bewitch (0.1.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial release
  * System metrics collection (CPU, memory, disk, network, temperature, power, processes)
  * DuckDB storage with retention and archival to Parquet
  * Terminal UI with real-time monitoring and historical charts
  * Alert engine with threshold, predictive, and variance rules
  * Webhook notifications

